{#
/**
 * Head: Favicon, Apple Touch Icons, Microsoft 8+ Tiles
 *
 * @author Travis Cook (cooktw@missouri.edu), Digital Service, University of Missouri
 * @copyright 2022 Curators of the University of Missouri
 *
 * Variables:
 * - icons_apple_mask_icon_color: (string) Color of mask icon for Safari on OS X El Capitan and up (optional, see default).
 * - icons_asset_url: (string) URL of asset directory (CSS, JavaScript, and template images) (optional, see default).
 * - icons_ms_tile_color: (string) Microsoft Windows tile color (see default).
 * - icons_short_name: (string) A short version of the site name (will be used under iOS homescreen icons and Windows 8+ tiles) (see default).
 * - icons_site_icon_color: (string) Color of icons used for Apple and social media uses (see default).
 */
